## Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `max_tokens` | int | {{ max_tokens | default(512) }} | Maximum tokens to generate |
| `temperature` | float | {{ temperature | default(0.7) }} | Sampling temperature (0–2) |
| `top_p` | float | 1.0 | Nucleus sampling probability |
| `stream` | bool | false | Enable streaming response |
| `stop` | list | null | Stop sequences |

